# Changelog Tracking

Maintain a changelog at `vsix/CHANGELOG.md` to track all changes between VSIX releases.

## After every fix or change

Append a single-line description to the **Unreleased** section at the top of `vsix/CHANGELOG.md`:

```markdown
## Unreleased
- Fixed hover connector alignment in ERD
- Added unmapped badge to sidebar
```

Keep descriptions short and user-facing (what changed, not how).

## When building a VSIX

Before packaging, move all **Unreleased** items under a new version heading with today's date:

```markdown
## Unreleased

## 0.0.2 - 2026-03-11
- Fixed hover connector alignment in ERD
- Added unmapped badge to sidebar

## 0.0.1 - 2026-03-10
- Initial release
```

Then bump the version in `package.json` to match.

## File location

The changelog lives at `vsix/CHANGELOG.md`. Create it if it doesn't exist.
